lines.text: See, old timer? You're through. Washed up.
You mean to say, I'm one of them there used-to-wasits?

[Imitating Rover]
Yes, I mean to say you're one of them there used-to-wasits.
Hey, D-don't imi... imi... mimic rover like that. He's sensitive.

[Imitating Porky]
Oh g-g-gee, I'm sorry to hear th-th-that. Nyah!
